HealthMap Alerts via
ProMED-mail <promed@promedmail.org>

[Certainly, the diagnostic test will be performed several times as
well as samples likely being sent to another laboratory for
confirmation. The country is facing some regulatory challenges
whether to vaccinate or not. The racing industry is a congregation of
horses, and if the disease presents a risk, then vaccination may be a
good choice. - Mod.TG]
